body_html: @drpngx Hmmm...It seems like those are from the contrib/layers folder, and git didn't merge the latest changes from master to this pull request after I moved my codes out of contrib/layers. body: @drpngx Hmmm...It seems like those are from the `contrib/layers` folder, and git didn't merge the latest changes from master to this pull request after I moved my codes out of `contrib/layers`. I ended up just replace the folder with the one I have from the latest master branch, hopefully this would not make other things break.
